          <a class="resource-chip chip-purple" href="https://www.amazon.com/Applied-Cryptography-Protocols-Algorithms-Source/dp/1119096723" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i> <span>Applied Cryptography</span><small>Bruce Schneier (Amazon)</small></a>
          <a class="resource-chip chip-purple" href="https://www.amazon.com/Cryptography-Engineering-Principles-Practical-Applications/dp/0470474246" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> <span>Cryptography Engineering</span><small>Ferguson, Schneier, Kohno (Amazon)</small></a>
